flowchart TD
  A[Start master session\nkvdf multi-ai evolution session master --watch] --> B[Load local governance state from .kabeeri]
  B --> C[Refresh Wi-Fi/LAN discovery via wifi_data_sharing]
  C --> D[Advertise master on network]
  C --> E[Scan for workers]
  D --> F[Collect discovered candidates]
  E --> F
  F --> G[Build worker pool view]
  G --> H{Any trusted or ready worker?}
  H -- No --> I[Stay in attention/warn\nkeep scanning]
  H -- Yes --> J[Ingest join requests / heartbeats / results]
  J --> K{Worker join request received?}
  K -- No --> L[Continue watching]
  K -- Yes --> M[Promote worker to trusted pool]
  M --> N[Materialize approved assignment packet]
  N --> O[Send assignment packet to worker]
  O --> P[Receive heartbeat packets]
  P --> Q[Receive completion/result packet]
  Q --> R[Acknowledge completion]
  R --> S[Review result locally]
  S --> T[Commit and push only from master laptop]
